conference.title: Early Bird Ticket Sale for PHPConf.Asia 2016
conference.summary: [PHPConf.Asia 2016](https://2016.phpconf.asia) is happening in Singapore on 22-24 August 2016. Tutorial Day on 22 Aug. 2 day single track conference on 23 and 24 August.
conference.content:
[PHPConf.Asia 2016](https://2016.phpconf.asia) is happening in Singapore on 22-24 August 2016. Tutorial Day on 22 Aug. 2 day single track conference on 23 and 24 August.
**Keynote Speakers:** Davey Shafik ([@dshafik](https://twitter.com/dshafik)) and Samantha Quiñones ([@ieatkillerbees](https://twitter.com/ieatkillerbees))
***Early Bird Tickets available now!*** (valid till 5 August). Visit <https://2016.phpconf.asia> for more details.
